def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item + bins) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.log(1 + np.sin(np.pi * item / bins))
```

```python
import numpy as np

def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return np.exp(item) * (item - np.mean(bins)) + np.cos(np.pi * item / bins)
```

```python
import numpy as np

def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:
    return (item / bins) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.log(np.sin(np.pi * item / bins) + 1)
```

